{title:Concrete Angel}
{artist:Christina Novelli}

Concrete Angel (Acoustic)
Christina Novelli
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aD8IY7Q_n-U
Work based on tab from VendettaFTE, filled just the missing parts and corrected some chords.

Standard tuning

Chords used:
[Em]     (022000)
[G]      (320003)
[D]      (xx0232)
[A]      (x02220)
[C]      (x30210)
[Em7]    (020000)
[Gsus4]  (320013) 
[Dsus4]  (xx0233) 


