Verse 1
          [Em]                 [G]                       [D]         [A]    
 Let me breath you in, and breath the words in your mouth,
                [Em]           [G]                [D]           [A]                  
inside your shivering, the silence shouts so loud.
[Em]             [G]                [D]       [A]                             
I just want to, I just want to stay around,
             [Em]              [G]                   [D]         [A]               
and while my heart beats I promise I won't let you down.


